{"id":"23027","name":"駛向第二次生命","rarity":5,"path":"Rogue","desc":"他彷彿落入深海，一切都離他而去，只餘空洞的思維在跳躍與掙扎。\n恐懼、不安、孤獨、黑暗、憤怒……那些感受沒有隨著肉身消散，反而以另一種方式保留在機械的軀殼之中，益發沉重。\n他聽到逝者的呼喚、聞到燒焦的氣味，電機的嗡鳴在他的耳邊盤旋、藍色的血液流向他飢渴的心臟……一些殘忍的記憶再次浮現，刻骨的仇恨化作黑暗中的微光。他循著光亮朝盡頭走去，用盡力氣浮出了水面。\n他睜開眼。一簇火花閃過，他聽到來自醫者的祝賀——\n「歡迎再次來到這個世界。」\n他握緊雙手，如今它們是冰冷的鋼鐵……\n他將不再為自己而活。","icon":"icon/light_cone/23027.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/23027.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/23027.png","ranks":{"id":"23027","skill":"苦航","desc":"使裝備者的擊破特攻提高#1[i]%，造成的擊破傷害無視目標#3[i]%的防禦力。當裝備者在戰鬥中擊破特攻至少為#2[i]%時，速度提高#4[i]%。","params":[[0.6,1.5,0.2,0.12],[0.7,1.5,0.23,0.14],[0.8,1.5,0.26,0.16],[0.9,1.5,0.29,0.18],[1,1.5,0.32,0.2]],"properties":[[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.6}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.7}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.8}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.9}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":1}]]},"promotions":{"id":"23027","values":[{"hp":{"base":48,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":26.4,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":21,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":105.6,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":58.08,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":46.2,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":182.4,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":100.32,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":79.8,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":259.2,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":142.56,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":113.4,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":336,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":184.8,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":147,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":412.8,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":227.04,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":180.6,"step":3.15}},{"hp":{"base":489.6,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":269.28,"step":3.96},"def":{"base":214.2,"step":3.15}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":5000},{"id":"114011","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":10000},{"id":"110191","num":4},{"id":"114011","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":20000},{"id":"110192","num":4},{"id":"114012","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":50000},{"id":"110192","num":8},{"id":"114012","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":100000},{"id":"110193","num":5},{"